{"tid":2127962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劇本已出現：港澳辦指將應特區請求提供必要支持 包括提高檢測能力","createTime":"2020-07-27T15:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T00:36:03.000Z","uid":3513,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bf64dc4bf2215257794c79b8c6657ca12e024bc0","tid":2127962,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"港澳辦指將應特區請求提供必要支持　包括提高檢測能力<br />\n<br />\n國務院港澳辦表示，香港爆發新一輪疫情後，中央政府高度關注香港疫情變化及防控工作，將應特區政府提出的請求，提供一切必要的支持和幫助，特別是提高核酸檢測能力，加快建立臨時隔離和治療中心等。發言人說，有少數人甚至是醫護人員在政治偏見和政治操弄企圖的驅使下，挖空心思拋出奇談怪論，甚至造謠污蔑，以阻撓中央有關部門及內地有關地方對香港抗疫的支持，這種為達到政治目的而罔顧市民生命安全的行為與「政治攬炒」同樣令人不齒。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-27 23:08:53 RTHK News<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"large\">無論你想唔想支那出手，接住落嚟個劇本一定係支共派吹風要維尼幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，柒婆出面感激爺閪出手幫香港抗疫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個武漢肺炎就係一場踩低香港，捧起爺閪嘅宣傳戰</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【獨家】《蘋果》獲密件揭林鄭向中央獻計 藉抗疫令建制選情轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200222/2N2J3KSNA2L5FVKFUU5S2QZMNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200222%2F2N2J3KSNA2L5FVKFUU5S2QZMNQ%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=57ce8398\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200222%2F2N2J3KSNA2L5FVKFUU5S2QZMNQ%2F&h=87c77fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200222/2N2J3KSNA2L5FVKFUU5S2QZMNQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n你地仲有無印象柒婆份密件？唔記得既話，我補返條link提下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cc6d3037c92b2befacb9c3be31517282cc33fb","tid":2127962,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"大陸真好<